<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>What</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: A Fresh Start Party<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>When:</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Saturday January 11th, 6pm Eastern<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Where:</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Toxxulia Forest, across the channel at the stone pillars leading into Kerra Isle <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>(/join party)</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Why:</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> To get everyone together for some fun!  <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>(In-character interaction)</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
Some of us have done some things we might regret.  For others of us, those regrets may be in things we haven't done, but feel we should have.  And then, some of us just like to party.<br>
<br>
So I'm throwing a Fresh Start Party, where we can all get together for a night and celebrate a year filled with new possibilities and opportunities for laughter and fun!  And since one of the things I regret was kinda not seeing anybody for over a month, I hope I can see some of the folks I've been missing as well as folks I've not been able to meet before.<br>
<br>
We'll have treats, we'll have drinks, we'll have games... we'll pretty much have whatever we all end up wanting to have!  Here's some of my ideas, please feel free to bring your own:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>1) A New Resolution Contest, and/or a Worst Mistakes Contest</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Try your tongue at One-Upsmanship or One-Downsmanship to prove YOU will have the best year, or are leaving behind the worst!  I personally put more importance on funny rather than true, though I suppose a tear or two could win you some points.  (I'll prolly just declare everyone a winner and hand out another round of drinks.)<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>2) Personal Fireworks Displays</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Oh sure, tinkers can make and bring their own, but those of us with magics can show off the fireworks WE can make when we cast!<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>3) Strip-Dice</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Since I invented this game because I wanted to keep the LAST open-party I threw from getting boring, we could always play it again!  (And no, rumors that I invented it solely because I was the ONLY girl there are... well, just funny! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   )<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>4) Drinking Contest</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Contestants are encouraged to bring their own brew!<br>
<br>
Well anyways, no reason to make this too structured, just show up when you want to and leave when you've had enough!  If you would like to attend but can't make it on Saturday, I've thought about throwing one on Sunday too if there's enough interest.  Just let me know!<br>
